data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom bi-level home situated on a desirable corner lot in a tranquil and sought after neighbohood! Spanning 1,762sf of living space, this meticulously maintained home boasts elegant hardwood floors, adding warmth and character to the inviting living spaces. The upper level features a well appointed kitchen that has been recently updated with painted cabinets, hardware and flooring. The living room exudes a a welcoming ambiance, complemented by abundant natural light filtering through large windows. Also upstairs, is a lovely dining room, 3 spacious bedrooms and completed updated hall bathroom! The lower level offers a spacious family room, 4th bedroom, launry room with access to the 2 car attached garage. Step outside off of the kitchen onto the tiered deck, a delightful extension of the living space, offering a serene retreat for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. The uppder deck, covered for your convenience and a lower deck exposed to the sunlight! This property is further enhanced by it's prime location with a friendly community, offer proximity to local amenities, schools, parks, shopping , restaurants, etc. Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously maintained home yours and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style and convenience.
